reviews.title: Beautiful, nice table
reviews.review_text: I was genuinely surprised by the overall quality of this table for how inexpensive it was! Assembly was very easy, the instruction manual is well written and contains QR codes for steps you may need help with understanding. I've assembled so much furniture it's insane, but this table has both quality materials and quality screws, etc (I was surprised their dowels are wood for this, as the cube systems Walmart sells usually have plastic) the table isn't real wood, but the finish has a nice grain texture to it. The table is very sturdy, and I really love it!!! I would absolutely recommend this, you can't beat the quality, the price, or Walmarts incredibly fast shipping!

reviews.title: Really nice coffee table for the price
reviews.review_text: I love the style of this coffee table and I would say you get what you're paying for quality wise. It is not the nicest material, but it is still sturdy and holds up well structurally. I really love this table.

reviews.title: Simple and elegant
reviews.review_text: This is a great coffee table. This works as a dupe to a much higher-end coffee table. It was fairly simple to build and is very sturdy. I've only had compliments on it!

reviews.title: Get it!

reviews.title: Chefs kiss
reviews.review_text: I absolutely love this coffee table. For the price, too? It's literally perfect. I love the look, the size is great. It's great for my apartment, it's not SUPER heavy so it's not impossible to move from place to place. It's genuinely the perfect coffee table if you don't know how you are going to decorate your place. It's great. It doesn't feel cheap. It's thick wood and it's very sturdy

Extremely easy to assemble Assembled it by myself in about 30 minutes Only thing wrong is it came with a few scratches on the top with the black chipped off. Other than that I recommend this coffee table.

reviews.title: Sturdy chic and versatile coffee table to level up
reviews.review_text: [This review was collected as part of a promotion.] Lightweight and sturdy. Each to assemble. I'm impressed with the bottom where it comes with 6 studs to prevent scratching of the floor. It's versatile and can be used as a coffee table or a tv shelf. The wood was very light which helped in assembling the coffee table together. The size is perfect as I live in a condo and it elevates my open kitchen living room format. I love how I can use the bottom rack to store all my junk food.

reviews.title: The simplistic, yet elegant, design looks amazing!

I enjoyed some of the little jokes they included in the instructions as well! The size is great and it fits well for what we needed it for. We already have a coffee table but this was perfect for our daughter's room to display/store some of her larger toys (as pictured)
